Text: crazy-torrent: Deja de postear links a otras paginas en torrents de otras personas. Hazlo en tus propios torrents. O no lo hagas. Es una advertencia.

Translation of mrspatula:

crazy-torrent: Stop posting links to other pages in torrents of others. Do it at your own torrents. Or do not. It is a warning.
crazy-torrent: Acabas de perder tu status VIP y todos tus comentarios han sido borrados. Si continuas con esto tambien perderas tu status Trusted...

Translation:

crazy-torrent: You just lost your VIP status and all your comments have been deleted. If you continue with this too will lose your status Trusted ..

I think you better listen to him crazy-torrent.
I wouldn't like to see your torrents removed from TPB as your one of the best uploaders on TPB
